data.name: broomtxt1.Text
data.value: You stuffed yourself inside the cabinet and hid like a coward. You're surrounded by a bunch of tools and bits. 'This closet is damn old.', you utter in annoyance as you wiped the dust that landed on your face. A few moments later, the entity barged in the room. It stopped and stood there looking for you. Out of nowhere, you feel your nose itch. Not even a second later, you let out a harsh sneeze that alerted the entity of your position. You're fucked now.
